ActIndian Act
SubjectCowessess Indian Reserve No. 73, Saskatchewan ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of the power to take an interest in lands within COWESSESS INDIAN RESERVE NO. 73, located approximately 150 kilometers east of Regina, Saskatchewan; and (b) granting the Company the required easement.
